snippet.title: Firebird - Steam version - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Firebird is another classically inspired arcade zap 'em up. This time we've taken our cue from the alien shooters of the late 1980's.

Firebird brings together a whole host of the features and effects we have all loved from the space invasion genre and puts them all together for some action packed, fast paced blasting chaos.

Developed by JimJams Games
